_sText: GG_CORRUPT_V1 by 2ToW @ Copyright studios Okay, this map is about an alley with boxes, few trucks. All props give good cover and time to reload your gun. There is an small building in the middle which you can get on by using the ladders. Info: -32 spawns -Alot cover -Good for gungame and fy. -I think its pretty "dark". Please, assess and comment!
